    "1200802": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kamisato Ayaka",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "This stall sells Prayer Plaques. It's an Inazuman tradition — you draw your wish onto a pentagonal piece of wood called a Prayer Plaque and pray that it will come true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sounds similar to the way people in Liyue release lanterns during Lantern Rite. Those are used for making wishes, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoshikawa",
                    "T": "Oh, welcome! Looking for Prayer Plaques? Every wish is sacred, and you've still got time to make yours before the festival ends!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Looks fun! Shall we give it a try?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Wait, there's writing and drawing involved? Count Paimon out, then... Paimon's head's feeling kinda fuzzy after eating so much just now... not the best time for an intense burst of mental activity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Two Prayer Plaques please, sir."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoshikawa",
                    "T": "Two Prayer Plaques for the young lady. There you go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Traveler, have you decided on your wish?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yep! How about you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoshikawa",
                    "T": "You can either draw a picture to represent your wish or write it out in words. Either way, once you've committed your wish onto your plaque, please hang it onto the Prayer Rack."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, so they'll be on public display!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Alright, {NICKNAME}, well, let's see what you got!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "That will do for mine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "May I see yours?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You got it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "#This is you and your {F#brother}{M#sister}, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "It's lovely."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#Yes. I want {F#him}{M#her} back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You'll be back together one day. Paimon believes it, and you should too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I believe it too. Your wish will surely come true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "And... I will keep you in my prayers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ayaka, what did you draw? Is that Tenshukaku?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "That's right. I wish for peace and happiness for everyone in Inazuma, and good health for my family and friends."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "*sigh* I do hope that wish can come true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Thank you, that gives me hope."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "*sigh* I think that might be all we have time for today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aw... It's time to leave already?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I'm afraid so. The festival is coming to a close."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Time flies when you're having fun... It seems to flow away from you like a rushing river... As precious and short-lived as a cherry blossom dancing in the wind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "It's time to leave."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
