    "1200806": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kamisato Ayaka",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Traveler, look, this stall's doing fortune slips."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "Miss Kamisato, hello there! You're out with friends today? What a rare privilege — welcome, welcome! Would you like to give it a go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Okay! How much is it per draw?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "Hehehe, I wouldn't expect you to know this, but the Yashiro Commission was very good to my uncle on my father's side at one point in time. Thinking about it, it was when your father was around, I think he dealt with it personally."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "So you see? How could I possibly take your money?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "What? A—Are you sure?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "Of course! If you like what you see, then please, be my guest. Same goes for your two friends here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Traveler, Paimon... What do you think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It seems like everyone wants to do something nice for Ayaka! So if they insist... who are we to resist!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "If they're offering, who are we to refuse?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm enjoying being a VIP by association!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Well, if that's how you feel, then... okay! We'll take you up on your kind offer, sir! Let's each do a draw."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "Alrighty then! Whenever you're ready."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shimizu",
                    "T": "Draw a slip and reveal your fortune!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
