    "1200807": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kamisato Ayaka",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "This food stall sells all kinds of Inazuman specialties. Anything you want to eat, it's my treat!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, it all looks so good... Is it okay if Paimon has one of everything? *chuckle*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Hahaha, of course it is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, but we don't want anything to go to waste. Let's try them one at a time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ayaka, Paimon wants those Dango!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Sure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll have one of those pink pancake things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh-huh, those look good too! Ooooh, but so do the Egg Rolls... Paimon will try an Egg Roll too, please!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Alright then. I too shall have a Sakura Mochi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Alright, coming right up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Mmm! This Sakura Mochi is just delicious!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Not bad, huh? It's one of our best-sellers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Please, sir, Paimon would like some more!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I don't know if it's rude of me to ask, but how is this kind of snack actually made?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Haha, you wanna try your hand at making it yourself? No problem, just give me a second and I'll write out the recipe for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A new recipe!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "A—Are you sure about this? If you share the recipe... isn't that tantamount to giving away your trade secrets... or something?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Well, it was you who gave Kiminami Restaurant that recipe for an overseas dish, wasn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Hehe, she and I are good friends. We trade culinary tips all the time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "Here you go, just treat it as me returning a favor on behalf of my friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "...Thank you so much, I will study it very carefully and try my best to do it justice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "You there, you want the recipe too? Go on, I can see that you enjoyed it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thanks, boss!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Murakami",
                    "T": "There's no greater feeling than creating delicious food with your own two hands. You should definitely give it a try."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I will!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Once I've learned how to make it... will you two be my taste testers?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, definitely! Can't wait!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Looking forward to it already."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Alright... I'll do my best!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
