    "1200817": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Traveler... Today was the first time in my life that I've ever been to a festival."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "You've known me for some time now... I think you understand my personality, don't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Knowing me... I just know that today could not have been such a happy day without you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "So, thank you. Today really meant a lot to me, and the memories will always have a special place in my heart."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Festivals are great! There aren't many rules, everyone has that smile that comes from deep inside, and... it's just so carefree and happy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "If I ever get the chance... Hee-hee, I wanna go again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'd like to go again, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "You too? Great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "You know, we're kind of similar, me with my brother, you with your sister."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "#Sometimes, I feel like I can relate to the determination you must have... to get your {F#brother}{M#sister} back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#Yes, {F#he}{M#she} means an awful lot to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#Finding {F#him}{M#her} is the whole reason for my journey."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Family bonds are inseparable — no one can break them... They are the most important roots we have in this world."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "#You will find {F#him}{M#her}. Come what may, you must never give up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I will always be here for you as your... Ahem! As your friend. I will always support you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thank you, Ayaka."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Today made me very happy, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thanks for being a splendid host today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "As long as you're happy, I'm happy."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
